TY  - JOUR
T1  - Introduction to the Special Issue on Marketing and Operations Management Interfaces and Coordination
AU  - Ho, Teck H.
AU  - Tang, Christopher S.
Y1  - 2004/04/01
PY  - 2004
DA  - 2004/04/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.1030.0171
