T1  - Managing NPD: Cost and Schedule Performance in Design and Manufacturing
AU  - Bajaj, Akhilesh
AU  - Kekre, Sunder
AU  - Srinivasan, Kannan
Y1  - 2004/04/01
PY  - 2004
DA  - 2004/04/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.1030.0177
